title: News 8 Highlight Zone - October 23, 2015
text:
News 8 Highlight Zone - October 23, 2015 Published On: Oct 23 2015 11:15:56 PM CDT Updated On: Oct 23 2015 11:34:34 PM CDT 
In Steve King's final year as head coach. 
Holmen has already sent him out in style with an M-V-C 
co-championship. 
??Now can his team get him some postseason victories 
to go along with that retirement gift?? 
Holmen a four-seed in Division two. 
opening up the playoffs facing five-seed DeForest. 
First quarter, DeForest wasting no time... 
Jadon Sackman bursting out of the backfield... 
56 yards down the sideline, no one is catching him... 
He's into the endzone, Norskies lead 7-0. 
Holmen looking to respond, on third and long... 
Connor Duncan hooks up with Zac Rusk... 
Rusk hangs on to the ball and keep the drive alive. 
Later that drive, Holmen's Seth Wilson takes the handoff.... 
He goes 16 yards for the score..,. 
Vikings miss the two point conversion, as they trail 
7-6. 
Keeping on the ground again, Sackman punches in his 
second score of the game... 
They lead 14-6. 
Still in the first quarter, more from the Norskies... 
Sackman having a monster day he punches in another 
score... 
All DeForest in this one, as they win 48-6. 
Also in Division two Tomah is at number-one in the 
state Waunakee. 
Waunakee's CASEY MARKSBERRY LOOKS FOR THE PASS DECIDES 
TO KEEP IT, RUNS 29 YARDS FOR THE TOUCHDOWN. 
Second quarter. 
MARKSBERRY HANDS IT TO HUNTER SCHOEPP. 
HE RUNS IT IN FOR THE SCORE.. 
Waunakee hands Tomah a 35-nothing defeat. 
When it's playoff season. 
it has been Logan's time to shine in recent years. 
The Rangers making it to at least Level three. 
three-years running. 
Logan a two-seed this season. 
opening up against three-and-six Madison Edgewood. 
Edgewood punts on their first drive. 
snap goes flying over the head of the punter. 
safety makes the score two-zip. 
That score holds until the second quarter when Trey 
Davis scores on the quarterback sneak. 
Big final minute of the half for the Rangers. 
Davis rolls out to his right and hits Jack Hinton 
from 27-yards out as they lead 16-0 with 34-seconds 
left. 
And then after an interception. 
Logan with the ball again. 
Davis on the last play of the half hits Nathan Baker. 
In what was a close game for most of the first half. 
the score all of a sudden is 22-nothing. 
Edgewood finds the endzone in the third quarter. 
Logan gets the points back at the start of the fourth 
on the Manny Buckhanan three-yard run. 
extra play at end - 3rd qtr - Jack Dunn 10 yard TD 
pass to Cody Link, 22-6 
Logan moving on to Level two of the playoffs with 
the 36-6 win. 
???Logan??? to play the winner of this game. 
Onalaska at Reedsburg. 
Hilltoppers hopiing to make the most out of a playoff 
berth after a sub-500 conference record. 
Final... 
And West Salem eliminated on the road tonight 42-to-7. 
In Division four. 
Black River Falls earning a three-seed and opening 
up at home against Tomahawk. 
Final...
